title: Episode 156: Bob Johnson – They’re Never Out Of Your League
description:
Show Notes:
As a former Playboy  Executive, publisher, and private investigator, Bob Johnson has seen it all when it comes to understanding beautiful women.

In today’s world of radical feminism, the #metoo movement, girl power and social media that gives women a 10-1 advantage over men, it can be a confusing time. In this episode, Robbie interviews Bob about the secrets most men don’t understand about the world’s most beautiful women and how to make yourself bulletproof in their presence.

In his book, They’re Never Out Of Your League – What I’d Learned About Beautiful Women As A Playboy Executive, Coach Johnson perfectly outlines what it takes to succeed with the most beautiful women. You can pick up a copy for free on his site.

Bob’s Website & Book: https://men-again.com/
